title: Fred Yakich
text: Fred Yakich (born in <a href="Sydney%2C%20New%20South%20Wales">Sydney, New South Wales</a>) is an Australian former <a href="rugby%20league">rugby league</a> footballer for the <a href="Manly-Warringah%20Sea%20Eagles">Manly</a> in the <a href="New%20South%20Wales%20Rugby%20League%20premiership">New South Wales Rugby League premiership</a> competition.
